propery.description: Charming home with 12ft ceilings, original woodwork, and hardwood floors ready for refinishing. Updated kitchen with tile and cork laminate counters. New sewer & gas lines. Detached 1-car garage with workbench. Small back deck, brick front porch, vinyl siding. Unfinished basement with shower, sink, laundry hookups. Newer furnace motherboard & hot water tank. Attic access. Electrical system coded. Shingle roof (approx. 10 yrs).
